MATCH_TOOL: Write
MATCH_PATTERN: \.superpowers/brainstorm/.*/content/.*\.html
ADVISORY: |
  Keep brainstorm mockup HTML simple. Complex CSS (deep nesting, pseudo-elements, animations,
  absolute positioning) can break rendering in the visual companion frame. Prefer: flat class
  hierarchies, inline styles for one-offs, minimal CSS. If a mockup renders broken, simplify
  the CSS rather than debugging the frame template. The simpler version (novel-v2.html pattern)
  always works better than the complex one.
